% StimPCIDIO96Globals - Declares global variables for PCIDIO96 system%%  NewStim can be configured to write stimulus display and triggering%  information over a National Instruments PCI DIO 96 card using %  Allen Ingling's pci_dio_toolbox, which must be installed and on the%  current path.%%  There is at present only one user-accessible option, and that is%  to turn this feature ON and OFF.%%  UseStimPCIDIO96        -  0/1 Should we attempt to use the PCIDIO96?%%  NSPCIDIO96             -  Data structure used by NewStim for communicationglobal UseStimPCIDIO96 NSPCIDIO96;